  <trk>
    <name>Geological hike to the Vieux-Emosson reservoir</name>
    <desc>Scenic hike to the 240-million-year-old reptile footprints and two high-altitude dams. Possibility of a spectacular train ride to the starting point of the hike.</desc>
    <type>hikingTourTrail</type>
